#. type: Plain text
#: use-case-birds-from-literature.en.adoc:100
msgid "Identify the different stakeholders participating in this project"
msgstr "Identificar las diferentes partes interesadas que participan en este proyecto"

#. type: Plain text
#: use-case-birds-from-literature.en.adoc:101
msgid "Identify their affiliation and assign each of them to a stakeholder group"
