#. type: Plain text
#: scripts/data-quality.en.txt:4
#, no-wrap
msgid "In this presentation, we are going to introduce some of the concepts that are important to understand basic data quality.\n"
msgstr "En esta presentación, vamos a introducir algunos de los conceptos que son importantes para comprender la calidad básica de los datos.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: scripts/data-quality.en.txt:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "// SLIDE 2\n"
